{"tha-ap206:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap206:0.2":"Kanikarapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap206:0.3":"Taraniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap206:1.1":"“Atthadassi tu bhagava, ","tha-ap206:1.2":"dvipadindo narasabho; ","tha-ap206:1.3":"Purakkhato savakehi, ","tha-ap206:1.4":"gangatiramupagami. ","tha-ap206:2.1":"Samatitti kakapeyya, ","tha-ap206:2.2":"ganga asi duruttara; ","tha-ap206:2.3":"Uttarayim bhikkhusangham, ","tha-ap206:2.4":"buddhanca dvipaduttamam. ","tha-ap206:3.1":"Attharase kappasate, ","tha-ap206:3.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap206:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap206:3.4":"taranaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap206:4.1":"Teraseto kappasate, ","tha-ap206:4.2":"panca sabbobhava ahum; ","tha-ap206:4.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap206:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap206:5.1":"Pacchime ca bhave asmim, ","tha-ap206:5.2":"jatoham brahmane kule; ","tha-ap206:5.3":"Saddhim tihi sahayehi, ","tha-ap206:5.4":"pabbajim satthu sasane. ","tha-ap206:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap206:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap206:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap206:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma taraniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap206:8.1":"Taraniyattherassapadanam catuttham. "}